The paper discusses the integration of near-data accelerators with main memory, which is a topic related to computer architecture (cs.AR) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). The paper also addresses challenges related to memory management and access, which are topics related to databases (cs.DB) and systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper demonstrates the potential of the system for machine learning algorithms, which is a topic related to neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
